===Etymology===
From ''[[bass]]'', '''low''' + suffix ''[[-oon]]'', '''large''', akin to ''[[-on]]'' in Romance languages

===Noun===
'''bassoon'''

#A [[musical instrument]] in the [[woodwind]] family, having a double reed and, playing in a [[tenor]] range.

